item.title: I Won a Notebook
item.description: This weekend, in a cursive workshop, I won a notebook from the russian language centre for the best handwriting. I’m glad :). I will put this notebook to good use. My Handwriting The Notebook I Won. The Cover Reads From Petersburg with Apathy and Indifference
